COVID-19 Status

As of 5:59PM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.2 thousand have died.

In the last day, 674 new infections were reported and 5 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 34.7 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 76.5% have their 1st shot and 27.8% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 8 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~8 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Aug-07 and fully vaccinated by Sep-07. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
